": {"rawForm": "SQuAD", "normalizedForm": "SQuAD", "offsetStart": 146, "offsetEnd": 151, "boundingBoxes": [{"p": 3, "x": 313.2, "y": 415.237, "w": 35.1491, "h": 9.4582}]}, "normalizedForm": "SQuAD", "context": "One difference between SQuAD questions and cloze-style queries is that answers to cloze queries are single words or entities, while answers in SQuAD often include non-entities and can be much longer phrases.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.5450726747512817}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.30964115262031555}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 0.14528611302375793}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999671578407288}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9944678544998169}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 0.26924553513526917}}, "references": [{"label": "Yang et al. (2015)", "normalizedForm": "Yang et al. (2015)", "refKey": 26}]}, {"rawForm": "SQuAD", "type": "dataset-name", "dataset-name": {"rawForm": "SQuAD", "normalizedForm": "SQuAD", "offsetStart": 27, "offsetEnd": 32, "boundingBoxes": [{"p": 3, "x": 504.851, "y": 428.786, "w": 35.1491, "h": 9.4582}]}, "normalizedForm": "SQuAD", "context": "Another difference is that SQuAD focuses on questions whose answers are entailed by the passage, whereas the answers to cloze-style queries are merely suggested by the passage.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.5108770728111267}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.41303667426109314}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 0.07608625292778015}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999671578407288}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9944678544998169}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 0.26924553513526917}}, "references": [{"label": "Yang et al. (2015)", "normalizedForm": "Yang et al. (2015)", "refKey": 26}]}, {"rawForm": "arti-\\ncles", "type": "dataset-implicit", "dataset-implicit": {"rawForm": "arti-\ncles", "normalizedForm": 